Two Liverpool soccer fans were
hospitalized with knife wounds after overnight clashes in
Naples, Sky News reported.  There was a series of skirmishes during the night ahead of
Liverpoolâ€™s Europa League game against Napoli today, Sky said,
citing police and British consular staff.  A 53-year-old man from Liverpool and a 27-year-old man from
